don't you?

03:51.136 --> 03:53.240
Please, let go of him.
This man is my client.

03:53.343 --> 03:55.066
Oh, I see, you think
you'll humble me, do you?

03:55.167 --> 03:57.557
Oh, no...! Look at them!
Look at what I have to put up with!

03:57.665 --> 03:59.803
Look at what they do
to innocent people.

03:59.871 --> 04:02.653
Trying to grab a feel.
Trying to grab me balls, you queer.

04:02.720 --> 04:05.207
You dirty perverts,
trying to get your rocks off.

04:05.311 --> 04:06.653
Drugs? What drugs?

04:06.751 --> 04:09.019
I've never done drugs in me life
and everyone knows it.

04:09.118 --> 04:10.711
Show them your credentials, Mike.

04:10.942 --> 04:11.891
Find the drugs.

04:11.998 --> 04:14.137
Give us a look, get them off.

04:16.285 --> 04:19.132
Find the drugs. Come on,
put your fucking hand up my hole,

04:19.197 --> 04:19.961
you poofters.

04:20.060 --> 04:21.206
Come on.

04:22.430 --> 04:23.541
Show 'em your credentials, Michael.

04:23.645 --> 04:25.979
Hey, you fucking faggots.
What are you afraid of?

04:26.044 --> 04:28.695
You do it in private,
but not here, you fuckers.

04:33.723 --> 04:35.130
Do you want any more, love?

04:35.195 --> 04:38.043
I'm grand unless there's dessert?

04:38.107 --> 04:39.154
Of course there is.

04:39.227 --> 04:42.041
Is that you in the newspaper da?

04:44.922 --> 04:45.870
Oh, can I finish that?

04:45.978 --> 04:47.700
Yeah, waste not, want not. Thanks.

04:47.769 --> 04:50.486
Oh, God, Michael, give it to me.
Give it to me.

04:50.585 --> 04:53.651
You know the way
all that red meat makes him hyper.

04:53.754 --> 04:55.160
Sorry, sorry wasn't thinking.

04:55.256 --> 04:56.685
Your father first.
Who earns the money in this house?

04:56.952 --> 04:57.999
Da does.

04:58.104 --> 04:59.282
They're all grand.
There's enough for everyone.

04:59.384 --> 05:00.977
They have to learn.

05:01.081 --> 05:02.804
you just better go to bed
when you're told tonight.

05:02.904 --> 05:04.081
Okay, mum.

05:07.896 --> 05:09.456
Have you got Lynch with you, lads?

05:09.560 --> 05:10.835
Check. We have him in our sights.

05:10.934 --> 05:12.428
Clothes on or off today?

05:12.502 --> 05:13.712
Fuck off.

05:13.814 --> 05:15.341
She's great.

05:19.477 --> 05:21.997
Say hello to your da.
Go on. Found him.

05:22.101 --> 05:22.995
Is that them, huh?

05:23.061 --> 05:24.141
Is that the two sisters?

05:24.245 --> 05:25.838
Oh, that's them all right, boy.

05:25.941 --> 05:28.755
Bet he was glad he didn't have to
choose between them, huh?

05:29.172 --> 05:32.019
Why choose
when you can have both, boy?

05:32.084 --> 05:33.710
Mind your mothers now.
Do what they tell you.

05:33.813 --> 05:35.055
See you tonight.

05:35.699 --> 05:36.560
See you.

05:37.044 --> 05:38.932
I'll call round later,
collect the kids, yeah?

05:40.756 --> 05:42.664
Hey, Tommy, get off the bleeding
bike, come on.

05:42.771 --> 05:43.502
Oh, come on, can I stay on?

05:43.603 --> 05:45.294
You know I can't take you
without a helmet.

05:45.395 --> 05:47.762
Please Auntie Lisa...
Come on, just one go.

05:47.860 --> 05:48.907
Come on then,
say goodbye to your da.

05:49.011 --> 05:50.287
Bye, da.

05:50.354 --> 05:52.558
Wave him goodbye.

05:56.178 --> 05:59.755
Look at daddy
going round and round.

05:59.825 --> 06:01.614
Say goodbye.

06:05.105 --> 06:08.846
Jesus, there's no way he can
shake us off, not out here anyway.

06:08.944 --> 06:10.853
So what's the point?

06:22.415 --> 06:25.862
Jesus. We're running very low
on petrol, Barry.

06:26.478 --> 06:28.071
Control where's
the nearest service station?

06:28.142 --> 06:30.597
