the petrol situation.

06:30.703 --> 06:31.564
He's getting out.

06:31.663 --> 06:32.939
Okay, lads,
I'll be right back to you.

06:33.038 --> 06:34.565
We're off.

06:38.030 --> 06:40.331
Right, lads,
the nearest petrol station's

06:40.557 --> 06:41.767
a good ten miles away, maybe more.

06:41.837 --> 06:42.731
Oh, Jesus.

06:42.797 --> 06:44.968
North east of the Bray Road.
Turn left for Bray.

06:45.069 --> 06:47.818
There's an Esso on the left,
about three miles outside the town.

06:47.884 --> 06:48.866
Keep in touch.

06:49.100 --> 06:50.791
I don't believe this.

06:51.052 --> 06:55.143
Ah for fuck, I told you
stop for petrol, didn't I?

06:55.211 --> 06:57.764
But, no, you said,
''We're fine, Con''.

06:57.867 --> 07:00.682
Look at him.
Sure, give him a wave, you wander.

07:31.368 --> 07:33.026
Where would you be
without the social welfare, huh?

07:33.287 --> 07:35.491
I couldn't agree more, Michael.
A vital few bob.

07:35.591 --> 07:36.867
Tony Brady.

07:37.127 --> 07:39.396
It's the difference between eating
and not eating sometimes.

07:39.464 --> 07:42.146
You said it, Tony. Good luck.

07:43.303 --> 07:44.830
Later.

07:45.255 --> 07:47.622
Michael Lynch.
And how are you today?

07:47.719 --> 07:48.188
Fine thanks.

07:55.462 --> 07:56.029
There you go.

07:56.262 --> 07:57.471
You're a gentleman
do you know that?

07:57.541 --> 07:58.556
Thank you.

07:58.662 --> 08:01.083
It's fellas like you
make the world go around.

08:06.052 --> 08:08.321
Right, we've caught up with Lynch.

08:08.420 --> 08:11.649
Told you he wouldn't miss out
on collecting his precious dole.

08:11.972 --> 08:13.051
Well, don't lose him this time.

08:13.155 --> 08:15.043
Oh, don't worry,
we're up his hole, Control.

08:15.139 --> 08:16.513
And we've a full tank

08:16.611 --> 08:18.618
Mr. Lynch won't be getting away
from us again today.

08:18.723 --> 08:20.609
Right, lads, keep in touch.

08:23.362 --> 08:26.297
I'll say one thing for him,
he sticks to the speed limit.

08:42.688 --> 08:43.799
Don't fuck about.

08:43.904 --> 08:45.693
Yeah, no problem, Michael.

08:46.848 --> 08:48.637
You're a mess, little brother.

09:00.030 --> 09:01.755
Relax, we're just passing through!

09:01.855 --> 09:02.870
Fucking hell!

09:02.943 --> 09:03.891
Excuse me, ladies...

09:03.999 --> 09:06.300
