14:05.183 --> 14:06.710
Sorry, bedtime stories.

14:06.814 --> 14:08.952
God! The Mansions again.

14:09.054 --> 14:11.225
I bet that put 'em to sleep.

14:21.085 --> 14:22.514
Christine asked me to ask you

14:22.780 --> 14:25.747
would you mind looking
after Tom and Shane tomorrow.

14:25.852 --> 14:28.219
She has to go into town to
get Breda her first communion gear.

14:28.476 --> 14:29.883
No problem.

14:34.619 --> 14:35.764
Are you ready for this?

14:35.866 --> 14:37.328
Oh yeah.

14:40.282 --> 14:42.137
I missed you.

14:56.631 --> 14:59.152
Fuck them! Don't answer!

15:03.223 --> 15:06.419
No, gotta call Billy,
tell him what's happening.

15:07.542 --> 15:08.949
Jesus! Fuck 'em!

15:13.622 --> 15:14.963
Who was with you at the bank?

15:15.030 --> 15:16.240
It was Stevie.

15:16.502 --> 15:18.922
No, no. Did Stevie drive the car?

15:18.997 --> 15:20.884
Stevie drove the car, right?

15:20.949 --> 15:21.897
That's right.

15:22.165 --> 15:23.594
And Tony Brady was with you, yeah?

15:23.700 --> 15:25.489
You see,
we know what you did, Lynch,

15:25.557 --> 15:27.563
doing jobs
while you're out on bail.

15:27.636 --> 15:29.523
And we have proof boy.

15:31.156 --> 15:37.265
All you have to do is say,
''Yes, that's just the way it was''.

15:39.411 --> 15:40.938
You drove to the courts
on a motorbike

15:41.042 --> 15:43.463
and then you switched
at the last moment, right?

15:43.538 --> 15:46.288
Fifteen minutes,
that's easy on a bike, Lynch.

15:46.706 --> 15:47.819
Give us an answer,
you fucking gobshite!

15:48.051 --> 15:49.992
All right, Con. Take it easy.

15:50.098 --> 15:52.912
Shall we start all over again,
shall we?

15:53.009 --> 15:55.879
You weren't with either of
your two wives Monday night

15:55.985 --> 15:57.195
we know that much.

15:57.297 --> 16:00.744
So, Michael, if you weren't
with the two ugly sisters

16:00.848 --> 16:04.077
don't tell me you were off
banging some other old slag?

16:29.645 --> 16:31.718
I realize you're not a golfing man,
Detective Sergeant

16:31.821 --> 16:35.052
but...
the Association of Inspectors

16:35.119 --> 16:37.256
and Superintendents Annual
Four Ball

16:37.325 --> 16:38.307
had to be cancelled today.

16:38.414 --> 16:41.261
Now, why do you think
it had to be cancelled?

16:41.357 --> 16:43.048
Well, I did mention to you, sir,

16:43.118 --> 16:44.939
that things like this usually
happen when we try to inter...

16:45.037 --> 16:46.946
Don't be the smart Alec with me,
Noel.

16:47.053 --> 16:48.231
I haev to tell you,

16:48.461 --> 16:50.632
