golfers here today.

16:50.700 --> 16:53.699
This is vital rest and recreation
for senior officers.

16:53.804 --> 16:56.389
Do you understand the importance
of this, Detective Sergeant?

16:56.459 --> 16:57.539
Well I do now, sir.

16:57.612 --> 17:00.100
Are you trying to tell me
''I told you so''?

17:00.524 --> 17:03.043
I'll tell you someting,
Detective Sergeant...

17:03.146 --> 17:05.896
I will not have
the reputation of the Garda...

17:05.962 --> 17:09.823
brought into disrepute
by these shenanigans.

17:09.930 --> 17:13.474
We will not be intimidated
by the likes of Michael Lynch.

17:13.578 --> 17:16.359
Are you listening to me now?

17:16.457 --> 17:17.602
Christine wasn't upset, was she?

17:17.673 --> 17:19.266
No, no, she's fine.

17:20.680 --> 17:22.108
