17:43.302 --> 17:46.750
Yeah, I do.
Aren't you a clever little shite.

17:47.527 --> 17:49.915
Can I put the patch on now?

17:49.990 --> 17:51.419
Don't wrinkle it.

17:51.525 --> 17:53.314
Job's worth doing.

17:55.781 --> 17:58.846
If a job's worth doing,
it's worth doing well.

17:59.493 --> 18:01.347
That's right... cool.

18:10.179 --> 18:11.390
That'll be the best way to park.

18:11.491 --> 18:13.312
Fucking brilliant parking that was.

18:13.410 --> 18:16.061
Shit!
A beaut.

18:16.163 --> 18:18.618
Hey, Tony, you drive like
a bleeding old woman.

18:24.769 --> 18:28.248
Fucking comedian...

18:28.353 --> 18:30.142
Mad fuck.

18:40.959 --> 18:42.105
Michael...

18:42.944 --> 18:45.463
...the new fella, Shay Kirby...

18:45.567 --> 18:47.127
doesn't bother you
he used to be in the IRA?

18:47.391 --> 18:48.984
